sentence: In early trading on Friday, shares of Walmart topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 0.1%.
Year to date, Walmart Inc registers a 0.9% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Goldman Sachs Group, trading down 5.4%.
Goldman Sachs Group is lower by about 14.8% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Nike, trading down 4.5%, and Home Depot, trading up 0.1% on the day.
